 the transition is left nearly\nunchanged. Utilizing a standardized set of measures, we compare to other models\nand find that WZDR is among the most successful at addressing the $H_0$ tension\nand the best of those with a Lagrangian formulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Oct 2021 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 20:36:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
