 the light curves. Our framework, used\nin conjunction with transient classifiers, will enable fast and prioritised\nfollowup of unusual transients from new large-scale surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Oct 2021 18:29:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2022 23:08:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-07"}
