ations by 2.40 times and one-qubit native\noperations by 6.13 times.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Oct 2021 02:28:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 17:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-05"}
